---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About | Mandy+Ally"
  description="About Mandy+Ally — fun, trend-savvy fashion that works for all ages and body types."
>
  <section class="page-banner">
    <h1>About Mandy + Ally</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="body-copy">
        <p>Mandy + Ally started with a passion to provide fun, trend-savvy fashion that works for all ages and body types. Our goals are to offer a wide selection of current styles with flair that accommodate your lifestyle and discerning eye while extending personalized customer service.</p>
        <p>We are always scanning the market for hidden treasures so we invite you to shop with us often. Hopefully you will fall in love !!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
